cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.SD, cs.HC 

This paper involves the analysis of web usage logs to gain insights into population-wide dietary patterns, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also involves spatiotemporal analysis (cs.CY) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Additionally, the paper uses time series analysis (cs.SD) and correlates nutritional data with hospital admission data (cs.HC).
